This email message is a notification to let you know that
a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the neat 
group.

  File        : /HyperNEAT_v2_6.patch 
  Uploaded by : evertwh2004 <evert@...> 
  Description : Patch file with modifications to compile/run Jason's C++ implementation (v2.6) under OS X. Requires MacPorts installation of boost, wxWidgets, python and zlib (see comments in the CMakeLists.txt files). The zlib project included in the original sources is no longer needed.
